Would you be available for a video chat on Tuesday at 7 for a first tenants
association meeting?

*- How are you aggregating responses, and where/how can we see them?*
We have so far gotten contacted by about eight apartments, and have only
collected apartment-related concerns from two or three tenants. We now have
a survey
